name: Mindful
description:
Yellow Garden Spiderlings negotiate their collective through space by way of carefully placed and organized threads. The collective is seemingly weightless, floating through the void between Daylily leaves, the collective's individual members mindfully construct the delicate threads of the structure to allow for the security and flexible movement through the space. (Argiope aurantia)

2018. Nikon D60, 55-200mm Lens.

Photographed in situ, without the use of artificial lighting or staging. Photoshop only used for resizing.
